OL,3,CWho are Hezbollah and why is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Israel-Hamas conflict?
OL,6,FITV News' Warren Nettleford explains
OL,7,Fthe origins of Hezbollah - one of the
OL,8,Fmost heavily-armed, non-state military
OL,9,Fforces in the world
OL,11,FSince Israel's strike on Beirut which
OL,12,Fkilled one of Hezbollah's top leaders
OL,13,Fin July, the world has waited with
OL,14,Fbaited breath to see how the militant
OL,15,Fgroup would respond.
OL,17,FHezbollah is a Shia Muslim militia
OL,18,Forganisation based in Lebanon, which
OL,19,Fsits on Israel's northern border.
