OL,3,CWho are Hezbollah and why is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Israel-Hamas conflict?
OL,6,FThe group has been the sworn enemy of
OL,7,Fthe Israeli Defence Force (IDF) for
OL,8,Fdecades.
OL,10,FHezbollah has regularly traded blows
OL,11,Fwith the IDF after conflict broke out
OL,12,Fbetween Israel and Hamas in October
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,FIts commander Fuad Shukr was killed in
OL,16,Fa drone strike in the southern suburbs
OL,17,Fof Beirut in July, in a move which
OL,18,Fmarked the first time Israel had hit
OL,19,FBeirut since 2006.
