OL,3,CWho are Hezbollah and why is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Israel-Hamas conflict?
OL,6,FBoth Hezbollah and Hamas are backed by
OL,7,FIran, which provides both with
OL,8,Ftraining, funding and military
OL,9,Fequipment.
OL,11,FThe two groups have become closer in
OL,12,Frecent years, with many Hamas leaders
OL,13,Fnow living in Beirut.
OL,15,FOn January 2, an apparent Israeli
OL,16,Fdrone strike hit an apartment in a
OL,17,Fbuilding in a Shiite district of
OL,18,FBeirut, killing Saleh Arouri, who was
OL,19,Fa founder of Hamas' military wing and
OL,20,Fhad headed up the group's presence in
OL,21,Fthe West Bank.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
