OL,3,CWho are Hezbollah and why is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Israel-Hamas conflict?
OL,6,FAlthough they often support each other
OL,7,Fin their sparring with Israel, the two
OL,8,Fgroups do have differences.
OL,10,FHezbollah is not a Palestinian
OL,11,Forganisation and is Shia Muslim
OL,12,Fwhereas Hamas and the vast majority of
OL,13,FPalestinians are Sunni Muslims.
OL,15,FWhat has Hezbollah done during the
OL,16,Frecent conflict?
OL,18,FHezbollah has launched near-daily
OL,19,Frocket attacks from Lebanon into
OL,20,FIsraeli territory, since the beginning
OL,21,Fof the conflict.
