OL,3,CWho are Hezbollah and why is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Israel-Hamas conflict?
OL,6,FIt has also allowed Hamas and other
OL,7,Fmilitant groups to carry out strikes
OL,8,Ffrom southern Lebanon.
OL,10,FUntil now, it has appeared that
OL,11,FHezbollah is not planning a full-scale
OL,12,Fmilitary attack on Israel.
OL,14,FIn a speech in November, the secretary
OL,15,Fgeneral of the group, Hassan
OL,16,FNasrallah, said Hezbollah is prepared
OL,17,Ffor all options, adding: "And we can
OL,18,Fresort to them at any time."
OL,20,FThe fighting would "not be limited" to
OL,21,Fthe scale seen so far, he said.
